data.title: Enhanced Blood moon mod crashes my server
data.meta_description: so I did a typo and instead of doing this command "/enhancedcelestials setLunarEvent enhancedcelestials:blood_moon" I typed this "/enhancedcelestials setLunarEvent enhancedcelestials:blood" so now my server crash loops. Here is the crash report I don't know what to do. ---- Minecraft Crash Report...
data.text:
